1
00:00:34,180 --> 00:00:35,940
=The Embroidered Truth=

2
00:01:17,519 --> 00:01:18,400
Wan, no!

3
00:01:20,700 --> 00:01:24,700
=Episode 20=

4
00:01:25,079 --> 00:01:27,439
From the day the pheasant's
head was severed,

5
00:01:28,040 --> 00:01:30,040
I never planned to live.

6
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:45,920
Murder!

7
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:47,719
Murder!

8
00:01:47,719 --> 00:01:49,319
Wu Lian killed me!

9
00:02:00,319 --> 00:02:01,200
She's dead.

10
00:02:02,040 --> 00:02:03,480
So what if she's dead?

11
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:06,480
Master Wu,

12
00:02:06,799 --> 00:02:08,520
the jailer knows you were there.

13
00:02:08,919 --> 00:02:11,919
We can't hide this.

14
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:19,919
What's wrong, My Lady?

15
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:22,599
I dreamed about Wan's death.

16
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:24,680
It's not true.

17
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:25,800
Dreams are fake.

18
00:02:27,599 --> 00:02:28,400
No.

19
00:02:29,599 --> 00:02:30,919
I need to see her.

20
00:02:31,080 --> 00:02:31,879
It's dark and slippery.

21
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:33,000
We'll go with you.

22
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,039
My Lady.

23
00:02:49,199 --> 00:02:51,039
This dead body is so heavy.

24
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:53,039
Ms. Meng looked thin and weak,

25
00:02:53,199 --> 00:02:54,639
but she weighs a ton.

26
00:02:54,719 --> 00:02:56,280
You're making jokes at a time like this?

27
00:02:56,439 --> 00:02:57,240
When the Princess Consort asks,

28
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:58,439
how do we explain?

29
00:02:58,759 --> 00:03:00,120
We know nothing, of course.

30
00:03:00,639 --> 00:03:02,120
We can't offend Wu Lian.

31
00:03:02,719 --> 00:03:04,280
He's the Princess Consort's favorite.

32
00:03:08,319 --> 00:03:09,120
Wan.

33
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:12,520
Why didn't you wait for me to save you?

34
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:31,039
(Wan,)

35
00:03:33,039 --> 00:03:35,280
(I won't let your death be in vain.)

36
00:03:41,919 --> 00:03:43,479
The Prince returns tomorrow.

37
00:03:43,639 --> 00:03:45,800
And you cause a death
in my manor tonight?

38
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:47,599
Please see the truth, Your Highness.

39
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:49,199
Meng Wan said

40
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:51,199
she knew some secret
about Lady Cheng'en,

41
00:03:51,199 --> 00:03:51,719
so I...

42
00:03:51,719 --> 00:03:52,479
Silence!

43
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:54,479
She is my cousin,

44
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:56,400
a Lady of Cheng'en Manor,

45
00:03:56,439 --> 00:03:57,919
soon to be a concubine to the Prince.

46
00:03:58,039 --> 00:03:59,280
What secrets could she have?

47
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:01,280
I was rash.

48
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:04,159
I only wanted you

49
00:04:05,280 --> 00:04:07,840
to shine at the Flower Festival.

50
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:10,719
I didn't think about the Prince
returning tomorrow.

51
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:12,759
Please forgive me.

52
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,040
Your Highness,

53
00:04:21,439 --> 00:04:24,480
I've been loyal to you for years.

54
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:28,639
You know my heart.

55
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:30,639
What good does that do?

56
00:04:31,399 --> 00:04:33,079
There are many servants in this manor.

57
00:04:33,279 --> 00:04:35,199
If word gets out that you
went to the prison...

58
00:04:36,279 --> 00:04:37,040
Wu Lian,

59
00:04:37,519 --> 00:04:38,720
I indulge you

60
00:04:38,959 --> 00:04:41,040
because you know what I want,

61
00:04:41,839 --> 00:04:43,279
and your skill is exceptional.

62
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:45,079
It pleases me.

63
00:04:45,519 --> 00:04:47,040
But since Ruoheng arrived,

64
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:48,720
you've repeatedly lost your sense.

65
00:04:49,279 --> 00:04:50,399
I know I was wrong.

66
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:53,279
If I keep protecting you,

67
00:04:53,439 --> 00:04:55,000
people will talk.

68
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:57,879
I deserve to be punished.

69
00:04:58,000 --> 00:05:02,120
But I'm like the grass and trees,

70
00:05:03,879 --> 00:05:04,680
cats and dogs of this manor.

71
00:05:05,519 --> 00:05:06,879
Your Highness,

72
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:08,399
I rise and fall

73
00:05:08,759 --> 00:05:10,040
with you.

74
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:12,519
Enough.

75
00:05:13,279 --> 00:05:14,319
I know about

76
00:05:14,439 --> 00:05:15,519
Meng Wan.

77
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:17,920
You had nothing to do with it.

78
00:05:18,519 --> 00:05:19,720
When the Prince returns,

79
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:21,279
cause no more trouble.

80
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:22,959
Otherwise, this isn't about
honor or disgrace.

81
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:24,279
It's about your life.

82
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:31,040
Well?

83
00:05:31,959 --> 00:05:33,199
Did you find Wan?

84
00:05:33,279 --> 00:05:34,040
Yes.

85
00:05:34,959 --> 00:05:35,959
Tossed at the mass grave.

86
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:39,600
I hear the Prince returns today.

87
00:05:44,879 --> 00:05:46,399
Lady Cheng'en, are you there?

88
00:05:51,279 --> 00:05:53,040
The Prince's troops have reached
the outskirts.

89
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:54,519
They'll arrive later today.

90
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:56,839
The Princess Consort
requests your presence.

91
00:05:57,279 --> 00:05:58,839
The Prince's arrival is a major event.

92
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:01,040
My Lady caught a chill last night.

93
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:02,399
When she feels better,

94
00:06:02,399 --> 00:06:03,680
she'll go to the Princess Consort.

95
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:04,560
But...

96
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:05,560
Tell Wenyue

97
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:08,000
I'll come after I wash and dress.

98
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:09,439
I'm her cousin.

99
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:12,480
I won't embarrass her before the Prince.

100
00:06:17,439 --> 00:06:18,480
What do we do now?

101
00:06:19,199 --> 00:06:20,000
Let's go.

102
00:06:20,399 --> 00:06:21,199
I'm coming too.

103
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:23,600
Xiaotao,

104
00:06:23,759 --> 00:06:24,800
you stay here.

105
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:28,680
See Wan off for me.

106
00:06:28,839 --> 00:06:30,480
I didn't know her for long,

107
00:06:30,519 --> 00:06:33,120
but I will never forget
her righteousness.

108
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:37,279
Let's go.

109
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:44,319
Master.

110
00:06:44,959 --> 00:06:46,199
Is the Princess Consort summoning me?

111
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:47,360
No.

112
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:48,480
It's

113
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:50,160
Lady Cheng'en.

114
00:06:55,759 --> 00:06:56,279
Follow her.

115
00:06:56,439 --> 00:06:56,920
Yes.

116
00:08:55,639 --> 00:08:57,039
Ms. Meng Wan is gone.

117
00:08:58,799 --> 00:08:59,799
Please accept my condolences.

118
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:07,240
She was clutching this.

119
00:09:12,799 --> 00:09:16,360
Wu Lian always keeps this on him.

120
00:09:20,279 --> 00:09:22,200
I don't know if Ms. Meng
told you this.

121
00:09:22,559 --> 00:09:23,639
She said if she's gone,

122
00:09:25,679 --> 00:09:26,799
I should take you to see someone.

123
00:09:28,759 --> 00:09:29,519
Who?

124
00:09:29,799 --> 00:09:30,919
They're at the Yehu Gang.

125
00:09:32,039 --> 00:09:33,200
You'll see when we get there.

126
00:10:04,960 --> 00:10:07,920
♪Night fades before the dawn♪

127
00:10:08,160 --> 00:10:11,160
♪Old vows still guide my hand♪

128
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:15,120
♪The past no longer binds♪

129
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:19,320
♪My heart still shines through dust♪

130
00:10:19,760 --> 00:10:23,880
♪Silent blooms, unchanged heart♪

131
00:10:24,720 --> 00:10:27,600
♪Bare hands weave through the frost♪

132
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:29,960
♪Shadows linger, rain returns♪

133
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:34,040
♪Honor crowns my weary soul♪

134
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:36,640
♪For your faith that never broke♪

135
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:40,960
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

136
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:43,760
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

137
00:10:43,760 --> 00:10:48,000
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

138
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:51,680
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

139
00:10:51,800 --> 00:10:54,440
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

140
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:57,040
♪One thought turns into ash♪

141
00:10:58,000 --> 00:11:03,360
♪No future left to write♪

142
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:06,240
♪If I never fall♪

143
00:11:06,280 --> 00:11:08,640
♪How could this waiting end♪

144
00:11:08,640 --> 00:11:10,000
♪If I bear no scars♪

145
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:12,320
♪How could I challenge fate♪

146
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:14,680
♪I knew there was no way back♪

147
00:11:14,680 --> 00:11:18,680
♪Yet I left this hope behind♪

148
00:11:18,800 --> 00:11:20,920
♪For your faith that never broke♪

149
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:25,080
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

150
00:11:26,040 --> 00:11:27,960
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

151
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:32,360
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

152
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:36,040
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

153
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:38,640
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

154
00:11:38,640 --> 00:11:41,000
♪One thought turns into ash♪

155
00:11:42,120 --> 00:11:47,360
♪No future left to write♪

156
00:11:48,240 --> 00:11:50,640
♪The lamp is out, you're gone♪

157
00:11:51,920 --> 00:11:54,040
♪Heaven and earth fall silent♪

158
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:57,920
♪If we meet again someday♪

159
00:11:58,360 --> 00:12:04,160
♪This longing sleeps beneath the snow♪

